00:54:43.000 --> 00:54:47.000
that has the flexibility to take the time to be with me?

00:54:47.000 --> 00:54:51.000
You have to tell them. This is important, not just to me, but to

00:54:51.000 --> 00:54:55.000
you as the boss and the executive leadership.

