Then it's been a lot of one-on-one

00:54:59.000 --> 00:55:03.000
conversations. I could try to make it not just

00:55:03.000 --> 00:55:07.000
about the data science part. I think a lot of the communication

00:55:07.000 --> 00:55:11.000
to build that relationship to get the ownership is really understanding what

00:55:11.000 --> 00:55:15.000
are the real underlying business problems. A lot of people

00:55:15.000 --> 00:55:19.000
